open slather
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a free-for-all, a free rein; anything goes
Origin:[none]
Register: informal

Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:-
Pronunciation:
Notes: (ca1920 p.c. R. Mason (1952)) compare DNZE earliest citation 1959
